headline: Communities Received Over $6.5M From Alliant Energy in 2025
summary: MADISON, Wis., February 26, 2026--Alliant Energy and its charitable foundation, along with the company’s employees and retirees, collectively contributed nearly $6.6 million and over 66,000 volunteer hours to various causes and nonprofits in 2025.
